reviewText: It says right in the print that it is a rewrite DVD!! So if not happy with it to bad I think it gives to the original format which to me is very cool!!
Bootleg copy of Hellsgate Picture quality horrible definitely a bootleg DVD
I received this disc and its a burned media copy, recorded from tape. There are parts the sound goes in and out and tape tracking lines are clearly visible during playback in a couple of spots.
